{
  "id": "adv_main_01_08_07",
  "title": "星見編2章12話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "えーと、つまり……みんなが男役になって\nお見合いの演技をするから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me get this right. You’ll all play the role of the guy‚\nand we’ll pretend this is my matchmaking date.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "私がそれを上手に受け流して\n断る練習をする……ってことだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’m going to practice skillfully\nturning down your advances… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さん\n事情はわかったんですけど、なんで私まで……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Err… {user}-san?\nI get what’s going on‚ but why am I also involved?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.90000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "悪い……ちょうどリビングにいたし\n相手役は多い方がいいかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry… You happened to be in the living room‚\nand I thought it’d help to have more people playing the guy role.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.23333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、ルールはみんな大丈夫？\nさっそく練習、やってみよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Has everyone grasped the rules?\nAlright then‚ let’s get started!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.082104537307586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 39.64877120397425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "お、おうおう姉ちゃん\nあ、あんたが、わた……俺のお見合い相手かい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey‚ lady.\nS-so‚ you must be the gir…girl I’m being set up with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.11543787064093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうです……は、初めまして\n佐伯遙子と申しま――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes. N-nice to meet you.\nMy name is Haruko Saeki――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.60205130609718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "お、俺ぁよ～、ここいらじゃ知らねぇやつはいない\nドデカいチームのアタマ張ってて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you know‚ there ain’t a soul around these parts who hasn’t heard of me.\nI’m Mr. Big Shot in this town…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.768717972763845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "アタマ……張って？\nこれってどういう意味なんだろう……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mr. Big… Shot?\nWhat does that mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1353846394305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "深く考えなくて大丈夫だよ、千紗ちゃん！\n書いてある通りに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t overthink it‚ Chisa-chan!\nJust say what’s written there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.86871797276385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなの？\nごめんなさい……や、やり直しますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really?\nSorry… I-I’ll start again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.03538463943049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "いや～……そもそもそんな時代錯誤な人\nお見合いに来ないと思うなぁ……来ても困るし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on… For starters‚ I doubt whoever’s showing up\nis gonna sound so old-fashion… at least‚ I hope not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4353846394305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……初めまして\n長瀬、琴……輔です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you.\nI’m Koto… suke Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.30205130609716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "こ、ことすけさん！？ 変わったお名前ですね……\nえっと、お仕事は何をなさって……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kotosuke-san? What an unusual name…\nUm‚ may I ask what you do for a living?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.62165909313596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "…………公務員",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m a civil servant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.32165909313596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "公務員！ 安定した素敵なご職業で……\nえっと、ご趣味は……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A civil servant! That sounds like a wonderfully… stable job.\nUh‚ and your hobbies?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4549924264693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "…………釣り？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fishing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2549924264693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんだめだよ！\nもっと盛り上げないと、お見合い成功しないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ Kotono-chan!\nYou’ve got to liven things up‚ or it’ll never be a success.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.38832575980264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "え？ ……成功、させるの？ 私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? A success? Do I need to…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.18832563264608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、趣旨が逆転しちゃってるよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ you’ve got it the other way around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.03832553727864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、僕ってお笑いの『ホットドッグさん』が\nすっごい好きなんですよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see‚ I’m a huge fan\nof the comedian Mr. Hotdog!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.77165887061193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "え、うそ！？ 私もー！\nすごい気が合いそうですね、ふふっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way! Me too!\nLooks like we’ve got a lot in common. Heheh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1716588706119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、じゃあ今度ライブ行きましょうか？\nチケット余ってるんで……ぜひ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you wanna go with me to see his next show?\nI’ve got an extra ticket!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.90499220394523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "い、いいんですか？\n……やだ、デートみたい……ふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you sure?\nOh‚ wow‚ it’s like we’re going on a date. Heheh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.13832553727863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……普通に\n……仲よくなっちゃった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re actually…\n…hitting it off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.171658870612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 167.67165887061196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "へー……まだ一度も男と付き合ったことないんだ\nこんなに綺麗な人なのに……もったいない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So you’ve never dated a man before.\nWhat a shame‚ such a beautiful woman like you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.771658870612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな……全然、縁がなくって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well… I’ve just never had any luck with men.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.871658870612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "俺だったら放っておかなかったのに、みんなバカだね\nいや、でもむしろ感謝するべきかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it were me‚ I’d never have left you alone. All those stupid men.\nWait‚ but I guess I should be grateful to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.2178947180852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_07-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "何色にも染まっていない君と\nこうして出会うことができたんだから……ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ I was able to meet you\nstill pure and untainted… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.91789471808517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
